eurs en coopération qui s’intéressent à ces questions.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Apr 2024) 0aInstitutional cooperationzQuébec (Province)xHistory. 0aInteragency coordinationzQuébec (Province)xHistory. 7aPOLITICAL SCIENCE / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Complete eBook-Package 2019z978311127268940uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9782760548961?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9782760548961423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9782760548961/original  a978-3-11-127268-9  ACUP Complete eBook-Package 2019b2019  aGBV-deGruyter-alles